# LayerZero Scan API Client

## Installation

```
npm i @layerzerolabs/scan-client
```

or

```
yarn add @layerzerolabs/scan-client
```

## Usage

```typescript
import {createClient} from '@layerzerolabs/scan-client';

const client = createClient('testnet');

client
  .getMessagesBySrcTxHash('0xc6071e98336996084a18a6c47ab38449e31d7d4b48040f35bbcd4106189e3036')
  .then((result) => {
    console.log(result.messages);
  });
```

Message type

```typescript
export type Message = {
  srcUaAddress: string;
  dstUaAddress: string;
  srcChainId: number;
  dstChainId: number;
  dstTxHash?: string;
  dstTxError?: string;
  srcTxHash: string;
  srcBlockHash: string;
  srcBlockNumber: string;
  srcUaNonce: number;
  status: 'INFLIGHT' | 'DELIVERED' | 'FAILED';
};
```
